wikibase-entitydata-text:
A peegyi ŋa tere la liŋk dɛta niŋe ko entiti tegerɛ. Sɔroo tere a entiti ID a URL poɔ, ne subpage syntax.
* yelbulo baŋganloo aplaai la yi a fo tɔretɔreba sagebo yelzu. ŋaa wuli ka a entiti dɛta na wa la lɛ na yeltuuri poɔ fo tɔretɔre naŋ boɔrɔ. Ka anaŋ wa e wɛb beraoza, o na e la HTML, ferɛ a fo beraoza ka o na leɛ daane gaa a buyi buyi entiti peegyi.
* Fo na baŋ wɛle la irikɔɛ dɛta kyaane yeltuuri ka foŋ paale a pɛll naŋ senne yɔlloo ko a entiti ID: Q23.json na leɛ wane la dɛta naŋ be a JSON yeltuuri, Q23.ttl na leɛ wa la RDF/Turtle, ane amine. Teɛbo yeltuuri la: $1.

wikibase-api-claim-value-unexpected: Fo koŋ baŋ tere tegeroŋ ka fõõ wa kuro maa so o ne PropertyValueSnak naŋ ba kyebe na e snak zu meŋɛ.
wikibase-api-cant-load-entity-content: Koŋ baŋ asɛsese yelbulo, leɛkaabo na baŋ sãã bare la.
wikibase-api-unresolved-redirect: A entiti teraa ID kyaare la leɛ daannoo, naŋ ba teɛ a yelbulo ŋa poɔ.
wikibase-api-editconflict: Maale yelbawontaa eŋ. Ba tõɔ kpari a pampana leɛkaabo.
wikibase-api-failed-add-sitelink: A siitiliŋk ba tõɔ na biŋ.
wikibase-api-failed-modify: Moɔbo na eŋ a bone kaama ŋmɛ la gbɛre.
wikibase-api-illegal-entity-remove: Entitiri koŋ baŋ sãã bare ne sazu-lɛvɛl teroo <var>remove</var> gbori biri.
wikibase-api-illegal-id-or-site-page-sel: A seŋ ka fo tere ka entiti <var>id</var>, bee a <var>site</var> ane <var>page</var> lantaaloŋ, kyɛ ta e a zaa.
wikibase-api-illegal-ids-or-sites-titles: Ka fo na tere la a bone "ids" bee "sites" kparre ane "titles" ko peegyi deree
wikibase-api-inconsistent-language: Kɔkɔre naŋ ba ara zi-yeni "$1" nyoɛ la (expected "$2").
wikibase-api-inconsistent-site: Siiti naŋ ba ara zi-yeni nyoɛ la.
wikibase-api-invalid-guid: Maa so o guubo ba tonnaa.
wikibase-api-no-external-page: A yiŋ tɔretɔre siiti "$1" ba tere peegyi duoro ko peegyi "$2".
wikibase-api-no-such-claim: Ba tõɔ nyɛ maa so o ŋa tɔ.
wikibase-api-no-such-entity: Ba tõɔ nyɛ entiti ne a ID "$1".
wikibase-api-no-such-entity-link: Ba tõɔ nyɛ bone naŋ taa a siitiliŋk ko a siiti teraa ane peegyi yuori.
wikibase-api-no-such-reference: Ba tõɔ nyɛ a sommo yizie ŋa tɔ.
wikibase-api-no-such-site: Ba tõɔ nyɛ a siiti ŋa tɔ.
wikibase-api-no-such-sitelink: Ba tõɔ nyɛ a siitiliŋk ko "$1" ka foŋ wa moɔra na maale badges eŋ.
wikibase-api-no-such-statement: Ba tõɔ nyɛ a yelyaga ŋa tɔ.
wikibase-api-not-supported: A irikɔɛ nandaa ba e bone a  entiti teraa naŋ areko.
wikibase-api-not-recognized-datatype: Dɛtapare da teɛrɛ ennɛ la kyɛ ka o boɔrɛɛ la bee ba leɛteɛre o.
wikibase-api-not-recognized-siteid: A siiti teraa wullo da ba nyɛ emmo.
wikibase-api-not-recognized-array: Ba teɛre eŋ la array, kyɛ ba nyɛ emmo.
wikibase-api-not-recognized-language: A kɔkɔ teraa koodi "$1" ba wa nyɛ emmo.
wikibase-api-not-recognized-string: O da teɛrɛ enna la striŋg, kyɛ o ba nyɛ emmo.
wikibase-api-param-missing: A irikɔɛ paramɛta "$1" wa boɔrɛɛ la.
wikibase-api-param-illegal: Paramɛtare ba tu sori sɛte toŋɛɛ la.
wikibase-api-permissiondenied: Fo ba taa a sori naŋ senne na e a yeli ŋa.
wikibase-api-wrong-class: Ba tori araa zie nyoɛ la.
wikibase-api-target-not-empty: A leɛ daannoo na baŋ kuri la yoŋ boŋkpale bee sãã bare entiti zu eŋɛ.
wikibase-api-target-is-redirect: A leɛdaannoo boŋkyooraa ba seŋ ka o meŋ e leɛdaannoo.
wikibase-api-target-is-incompatible: Moɔ na leɛdaane gaa entiti naŋ e pare yuo.
wikibase-api-cant-redirect: Koŋ baŋ kuri leɛdaannoo (ane lɛ bonso leɛdaannoo yi a entiti ŋa tɔ soba ba taa are teroo zaa).
wikibase-self-conflict-patched: Fo maale eŋ wa kparre eŋ la a leɛkaabo paalaa, na diire fõõ meŋɛ daŋ maale tɛgere.
wikibase-conflict-patched: Fo maale eŋ wa kparre eŋ la a leɛkaa baaraa eŋɛ.
wikibase-save-unresolved-redirect: Kyaare la ba leɛ maale daannoo yi $1 te tɔ $2 kyɛ moɔrɔ na biŋ tɛgebo.
wikibase-entity-summary-restore: La leɛ biŋ a leɛkaabo [[Special:Permalink/$3|$3]] ne [[Special:Contributions/$4|{{GENDER:$4|$4}}]]
wikibase-entity-summary-undo: Leɛ a leɛkaabo puori [[Special:Diff/$3|$3]] ne [[Special:Contributions/$4|{{GENDER:$4|$4}}]] ([[User talk:$4|yeli]])
wikibase-no-direct-editing: Daadaa maale eŋ tɔge la yoe vori poɔ $1
wikibase-noentity: A entiti ŋa ba tona. Fo na baŋ [{{fullurl:{{#Special:Log}}|page={{FULLPAGENAMEE}}}} wɛlle a lɔgere naŋ yitaa] na bɔ zie onaŋ gaa.
wikibase-noentity-createone: Fo meŋ na baŋ [[$1|kuri la bompaalaa]].
wikibase-special-mergeitems-error-prefix: A boma ba tõɔ lantaa. A ɛɛrɔ ama la wa;
wikibase-listdatatypes-wikibase-item-bod: Liŋk gaa boŋyobo a progyɛte eŋɛ. Ka tegeroŋ wa eŋ, a progyɛte "bone" yoe vori na bɔ la bommanne.
wikibase-listdatatypes-wikibase-property: Liŋk eŋ boma naŋ be a progyɛte. Ka tegeroŋ wa eŋ, a progyɛte "boma" yoe vori na bɔ la bommanne.
wikibase-listdatatypes-commonsmedia-body: Liŋk ko pɛll binnii naŋ be Wikimidia Kommons. Ka tegeroŋ wa eŋ, a pɛll' yoe vori Kommons eŋɛ na weɛre bɔ la pɛllɛ naŋ de taa.
wikibase-listdatatypes-globe-coordinate-:
Litiral dɛta ko gyogarapikal vuoaraa teraa naŋ e latitude-longitude ayi gms poɔ bee dɛzimale degeree ko a stellar enda teraa. Difiliti ko "Earth" ane "WGS84". O paale la irizolosiŋ ane voteraa.
* latitude – empilizit lombo fɔrɔ (float, dms, dm, dd) ko a koodinet striŋgye, daannoo naŋ e la daŋ biŋ bondemannaa bee tage biŋ niŋe bondemannaa N/S
* longitude – empilizit lomboe ayi soba (float, dms, dm, dd) ko a koodinet striŋgye, daannoo naŋ e la daŋ biŋ bondemannaa bee tage biŋ niŋe bondemannaa E/W
* donɛɛ zaa – ɛge-pilizit (?) dɛta tegeroŋ, naŋ tere e stellar endaa naŋ difiliti ko andonɛɛ "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q2"
* prisisiŋ - nambare prisisiŋ ko a koodinet
wikibase-listdatatypes-geo-shape-body: Liŋk ko gyogarapi mapo dɛta naŋ biŋ Wikimidia Kommons poɔ (bee konfigie wiki mine). Nyɛ "https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Help:Map_Data" na nyɛ sɛgere yaga kyaare mapo dɛta.
wikibase-listdatatypes-tabular-data-body: Liŋk ko dɛta tori binnaa wikimidia Kommons poɔ (bee konfigie wiki mine). Nyɛ "https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Help:Tabular_Data" na nyɛ sɛgere yaga kyaare dɛta toraa.
wikibase-listdatatypes-quantity-body:
Litiral dɛta ŋmɛ la gbɛre ko a semmo na naŋ e boŋyeni ko kyɛlee kaŋa pare naŋ kyaane. A kyɛlee mɛŋɛ na gaa la a dɛta tegeroŋ na naŋ eŋ. 
* noɔre ŋaa – a striŋgye empilizit lombori (mapping of unit prefix is unclear)
* kyɛlee – a striŋgye empilizit lombori naŋ difilit ko "1" (mapping to standardizing body is unclear)
* duobomaraa - semmo duobo maraa 
* sigibomaraa - semmo sigibo maraa
wikibase-listdatatypes-monolingualtext-b:
Litiral dɛta zigbuli ko syriŋgye naŋ ba leɛre eŋ kɔkɔ yobo. A striŋgye ŋa tɔ maŋ mannewuli la dayeni kyɛ la leɛ toŋ ne yɔ kɔkɔɛ zaa. Tipikal tontonne e la gyogarapikal yoe naŋ sɛge ne lokal kɔkɔre, wulwulo ko boma mine, kɛmeŋkal fɔɔmɛla bee Latin scientific yuori.
* kɔkɔre – ɛge-pilizit tegeroŋ naŋ wulo a kɔkɔre kyaare a sɛgere lombori
* tegeroŋ – ɛge-pilizit tegeroŋ ko a kɔkɔre veereŋ kyaare striŋgye
wikibase-listdatatypes-multilingualtext-:
Litiral dɛta ŋmɛ la gbɛre ko sriŋgye na seŋ ka o leɛre eŋ kɔkɔ yobo poɔ. Topikal toŋ ne la entiti yuori ko andonɛɛ zaa boɔbo naŋ taa non-lokal sɛgere fɔɔm. Ana na baŋ taa la tɛɛtɛɛ a kɔkɔre poɔ ne a sɛgere pɛll sisitim zaa can.
* kɔkɔre – empilizit tegeroŋ naŋ wulo a kɔkɔre ko a sɛgere lombori
* tegeroŋ – empilizit tegeroŋ ko a kɔkɔre veereŋ pukyaare striŋgye
wikibase-listdatatypes-string-body:
Litiral dɛta zigbuli ko glyphs striŋgye. Topikal tontonne la wuliwulli na naŋ taa sɛgere fɔɔm naŋ ba zenɛ kaara a kanna kɔkɔre.
* tegeroŋ - ɛge-pilizit tegeroŋ ko a kɔkɔre pukyaaroo veereŋ striŋgye
wikibase-listdatatypes-time-body:
Litiral dɛta zigbuli ko a pont wagere poɔ data. Naŋ e bebi teraa ane wagere ne prisisiŋ mine ane torebogiri. A wagere biŋ la poŋ a kalinda model pukyaaraa eŋɛ.
* wagere – ɛge-pilizit tegeroŋ ko pont wagere poɔ, naŋ areko e wagere nu mare yinni ISO 8601, e.g. +2013-01-01T00:00:00Z. A yuoni maŋ goligoli la ane padded na yi 4 ane 16 nambarre.
* wagere tonaa – ɛge-pilizit tegeroŋ naŋ e entigya. Wagere tonaa duoro naŋ e offset yi UTC miti poɔ.
* sɛre – ɛge-pilizit entigya tegeroŋ ko lɛ na kyɛlɛɛ naŋ na la a wagere puori lɛ na naŋ naa la. A prisisiŋ la maŋ tere a kyɛlee.
* wa baare – ɛge-pilizit entigya tegeroŋ ko lɛ na kyɛlɛɛ noɔre seɛre a wagere teraa na o naŋ na baŋ e. A prisisiŋ la maŋ tere a kyɛlee.
* prisisiŋ – ɛge-pilizit tegeroŋ enkoodi eŋ soɔtint poɔ. A nambare taa la ama naŋ tu muni: 0 - yuomo biliyoŋ, 1 - yuoŋkɔɔre miliyoŋ, ..., 6 - milinu, 7 - yuoŋkɔɔre ayi vuo, 8 - yuomo naŋ pare, 9 - yuoni, 10 - kyu, 11 - bebiri, 12 - gogo, 13 - miti, 14 - mitipronii.
* kalindarmodel – ɛge-pilizit tegeroŋ teraa naŋ e a URI. O wulo la a kalinda model wagere nu mare.
wikibase-listdatatypes-url-body: Litiral dɛta zigbuli ko a URL. URLs feerɛɛ la ko a protokol ane meŋ teɛbo ko yiŋ liŋkere wikisɛgere poɔ.
wikibase-listdatatypes-external-id-body: Litiral dɛta zigbuli ko yiŋ bonwulo. Yiŋ bonwulli na baŋ liŋk la otomatikal gaa otoriteeti yizie na yi gbaŋgbale.
wikibase-listdatavaluetypes-generalbody: A tegeroŋ tɔ ko a dɛta pare ŋa la $1.
wikibase-concept-uri-tooltip: URI na naŋ wulo a nyaabo manne la a bone ŋa
wikibase-pageimage-helptext: A enfoni ŋa de yi la a yelyaga ko a bone ŋa. Fo na baŋ yelle la a enfuoni ka fõõ leɛre a yelyaga.

Yelbulo pare ba de taa:
Koŋ baŋ wuli yelbulo
wikibase-entity-not-viewable: A yelbuli teree pare ŋa tɛ "$1" ba e entiti ane wikibeesi koŋ baŋ ere o.
wikibase-pageinfo-subscription: Wiki's neɛ la nu eŋ a entiti ŋa
wikibase-pageinfo-wb-claims: Yelyaga noɔre naŋ seŋ lɛ a entiti ŋa poɔ
wikibase-pageinfo-wb-identifiers: Yiŋ wulo noɔre yelyaga a entiti ŋa poɔ
wikibase-search-namespace-mix: Gyɛrɛ entiti ane atekele yoe vori peɛre bɔ poɔ pampana ba are tee. Entiti yoe vori yoŋ la na peɛre bɔ.
wikibase-search-config-notfound: Sɛgere zaa gbuli boɔbo konfigiriseŋ ba kyebe: $1
wikibase-search-config-badclass: Ba soma yel-peɛre soore meɛbo voaraa: $1
wikibase-refresh-for-missing-datatype: $1 dɛta tɔ kye a lokal tɔretɔre gampɛle sɛgere poɔ. A ŋaa na baŋ yi la gampɛlɛ sɛgere kore zie.  Moɔ kyɛ iriferɛse fo braza kpeɛŋaa, ana gaŋ lokal boŋkore binni bare (Ctrl-Shift-R bee Cmd-Shift-R brazare kponzie poɔ) na leɛmaale a yelwonaa.
wikibase-entity-save-error-message: Fo leɛmaale na ba tõɔ na yi gbaŋgbale. Fo na la baŋ neɛ la a gbaŋgbale dabiri la maale.
wikibase-tainted-ref-popper-text: A yelyaga ŋa tegeroŋ wa leɛmaale la, kyɛ a sommo yiziiri na ne a zu naŋ la. Fo na baŋ iri la a kpaamo ŋa ka a sommo yiziiriŋ naŋ wa tori.
wikibase-tainted-ref-popper-title: Na e sommo yizie/tegeroŋ nyɛrɛɛ taa
wikibase-tainted-ref-popper-help-link-ti: Soŋ peegyi ne begenyɔgere ŋa tɔ
wikibase-tainted-ref-tainted-icon-title: A yelyaga ŋa taa la yelsɔgle wonni.
wikibase-setclaim-warning-duplicatemains: Snak zu pullii nyɛɛ la. Yelyaga ba de paale.
wikibase-editentity-warning-serializeres: Ba tõɔ na e entiti dɛta tutaa na nyɛ yiibu duoro.
wikibase-federated-properties-save-api-e: Fo bimmo ŋmɛ gbɛre yi a gbɛɛ ŋmɛɛ irikɔɛ ko a fɛderɛseŋ wiki yizie.
wikibase-federated-properties-source-wik: Yelyaga kyaare a bone ŋa ba kyebe pampana yi gbɛ ŋmɛ irikɔɛ ko a fɛderɛseŋ wiki yizie. Sɔroo iriferɛse a peegyi.
wikibase-federated-properties-special-li: A Wikibeesi ŋa tona ne la fɛdere boma yi yiŋ yizie. Fo na baŋ asɛses la a $1.
wikibase-federated-properties-leaving-si: A ŋa e la fɛdere boma. Ba na leɛdaane fo la gaa $1 ka fo na kaa yɛlɛ kyaare o.
Ta la wuli ma a masɛgye ŋa la maale
wikibase-federated-properties-edit-reque: Fo koŋ baŋ maale a yelyaga ŋa eŋ a yi gbɛŋmɛ irikɔɛ ko a fɛdereseŋ wiki yizie.
wikibase-federated-properties-federated-: Fo koŋ baŋ yeli ne Fɛderete boma neŋ API ŋa.
wikibase-federated-properties-failed-req: A irikɔɛ ŋmɛ la gbɛre yi gbɛŋmɛ irikɔɛ ko a fɛdereseŋ yizie wiki.
